{"tid":212983,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（以事論事）真心 領養定購買","createTime":"2017-04-22T20:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T10:16:25.000Z","uid":41971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28d2969f5f6025f1764cb0fa5bc02c47e6b51638","tid":212983,"uid":41971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T20:12:47.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲同我分析下"},{"pid":"a6327fa2b6ab51ab7d18bcadd8a3e8757f0f33b2","tid":212983,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T20:22:22.000Z","msg":"領養到幼兒期寵物我就會領養<br />\n<br />\n否則會買"},{"pid":"30e4927f2a85e3770b5967ebf3cc8499d0bdb6b1","tid":212983,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T22:08:48.000Z","msg":"合眼緣。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一日上黎咩<br />\n爬下文，大把討論<br />\n你開個咁嘅post , 又係搵交鬧架咋"},{"pid":"42cb7bf08302fffb461a1d87680763b7b1cca9f8","tid":212983,"uid":84021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:50:09.000Z","msg":"領養"},{"pid":"8ae067c91a38a0a7435ec48962344a11f335882e","tid":212983,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"買"},{"pid":"6a1280ba80d230472d42e1f5a51e54030083b0d8","tid":212983,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"差唔多"},{"pid":"1ce7be697e90d2d5424981da93780eb0c954b526","tid":212983,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"合眼緣又比我領到佢當然好<br />\n有時真係係店搵到都冇計,合眼緣唔係咁易的<br />\n當然如果至在幫助小動物既人唔會理"},{"pid":"1c371087b595eb1f219a736dca40d7c29d1fa300","tid":212983,"uid":29127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"合眼緣<br />\n同埋你真係會好好照顧佢，唔好棄養<br />\n咁買同領養都無所謂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：領養左兩隻貓貓"},{"pid":"c401d86115e1fc818c8b7882db9514965ed8f76c","tid":212983,"uid":83394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"領養啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然領養既狗同狗場既狗既命運差唔多，但係啲錢廢事比啲扑街狗販賺"},{"pid":"75b8cae7c6fb51fb97bf3596cf5a39e7a2ded6c0","tid":212983,"uid":60648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"睇你係咪想養名種貓<br />\n<br />\n唔係既話就去領養啦"},{"pid":"2d8361a0168b3f9d920bbe468ead40e505aa00aa","tid":212983,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"領養到就領養, 就算有病起碼一早知.<br />\n<br />\n買就九成有暗病, 睇醫生一年都幾皮."},{"pid":"70516b8e4ebee326e160e7e15d1234cce3735907","tid":212983,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"最好領養 但又唔反對買"},{"pid":"9e35b56b883a6b213d4deee3d85fb06918547566","tid":212983,"uid":54901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"領養，生命係唔應該用錢買返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9ec66d8bb5bb02fb72ab755b612e588a933755","tid":212983,"uid":13892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"領導<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算買，都應該上網搵信譽好嘅breeder<br />\n而唔係去街邊寵物店<br />\n基本上寵物店都係逼啲動物係咁交配做生殖機器<br />\n你想養寵物都係因為鍾意動物姐，鍾意動物嘅話就唔好助長呢啲會害到動物嘅無良鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0104cf88c0be14c68dbbe473299c1dd1f542125f","tid":212983,"uid":13892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"同埋寵物店嘅動物真係病痛都多啲<br />\n因間又要洗好多錢去醫佢<br />\n一個唔好彩，醫唔好，盞自己心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052ad237b09c3328fc6b78b43b2c02c2ca8fbf8c","tid":212983,"uid":13892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算買，都應該上網搵信譽好嘅breeder<br />\n而唔係去街邊寵物店<br />\n基本上寵物店都係逼啲動物係咁交配做生殖機器<br />\n你想養寵物都係因為鍾意動物姐，鍾意動物嘅話就唔好助長呢啲會害到動物嘅無良鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f6cc5c60f32edd33aa38de34965da00516b9b59d","tid":212983,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"領養/發動技能<br />\n<br />\n不過要去SPCA 抵制搬龍門一言堂既貓義工<br />\n上網睇唔岩既 試下去總部 好似會多好多<br />\n<br />\n如果你特別鐘意某d品種 就去搵breeder買<br />\n同街買差幾千蚊度 但睇醫生都慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c6972cb62dfec8f698c46e3c6d4c527052d3f8","tid":212983,"uid":12259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"買<br />\n有興趣既永遠俾人領養左<br />\n買既少麻煩"},{"pid":"c2cec83a2b59aa965ed04287a43af7db27a79f5b","tid":212983,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"合眼緣<br />\n偏向買<br />\n因為義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f84f6b9d245f1780c0ffe45a07832ac2fe2811","tid":212983,"uid":93937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"傾向領養，去有認可既機構，唔係D 亂捉動物無本生利果D<br />\n有D人鐘意某種品種而又好少會有領養，要買既去有信譽既舖<br />\n<br />\n覺得為呢D而嘈好無謂，無論邊樣都係有心有力先好養"}]}